oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Century II: J. D. Sumner & The Stamps
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Presley, Elvis, 1935-1977; Sumner, J. D. (John Daniel); Stamps Quartet; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing a Century II Promotions / Talent Agency show with J. D. Sumner and the Stamps at a commemorative performance to Elvis. Poster features metal photoplates of J. D. Sumner, the Stamps, Elvis Presley's last official limousine, and Elvis with J. D. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/20606.
